}],["$","tbody",null,{"children":[["$","tr",null,{"className":"border-b border-slate-900","children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2 pr-4","children":"原油 ($/桶)"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2 pr-4","children":80}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2 pr-4","children":115}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"className":"border-b border-slate-900","children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2 pr-4","children":"碳价 ($/吨CO2)"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2 pr-4","children":90}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2 pr-4","children":115}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"className":"border-b border-slate-900","children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2 pr-4","children":"补贴 ($/升)"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2 pr-4","children":"0.50"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"py-2 pr-4","children":"0.55"}]]}]]}]]}]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300","children":"这个冲击场景的含义：航司优先削减低利润短途运力，同时对SAF成本竞争力更敏感。"}]]]}]]}]
9:["$","section",null,{"id":"event-overview","className":"mt-8 scroll-mt-16","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-white","children":"事件概述与深层逻辑"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 p-6","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-slate-300","children":["2026年4月21日，汉莎集团的削减2万航班公告，从表面上看是一项成本控制措施。但这背后隐藏着一个更深的经济学信号：",["$","strong",null,{"children":"短途航线的低利润率已无法在高油价环境中维持"}],"。"]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-slate-300","children":"对于汉莎而言，燃油成本占总运营成本的20-30%。当油价从$80/桶跳升至$115/桶（上升43%）时，短途航线的单位成本陡然上升30-35%。在竞争激烈的欧洲短途市场，廉价航空公司（如瑞安航空）已经通过规模与效率压低票价，汉莎难以快速提价来抵消成本上升。因此，削减低利润运力成为一个理性但痛苦的选择。"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-slate-300","children":["然而，这个事件的真正意义在于：它标志着传统航空业运营模式的一个转折点。削减航班虽然是短期应对，但从长期看，汉莎等欧洲航司的未来竞争力取决于能否快速转向可持续航油（SAF）。因为当油价维持在110-130美元/桶时，",["$","strong",null,{"children":"SAF成本与传统喷气燃料的差异会快速收窄"}],"，这将打开一扇新的成本优化之门。"]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300","children":"同时，欧盟ReFuelEU指令即将在2025年生效，要求航空燃油中SAF掺混比例从2025年的0.7%逐步升至2030年的6%。这意味着SAF从一个可选项变成了强制性合规要求。在这个背景下，汉莎的减班决定可以被重新解读为：航司正在为能源结构的转变而调整战术。"}]]}]]}]
a:["$","section",null,{"id":"fuel-cost-breakdown","className":"mt-8 scroll-mt-16","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-white","children":"航空燃油成本分解与德国溢价"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-sky-300","children":"Jet-A-1成本结构"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-slate-300","children":"当前（2026年4月），全球标准喷气燃料Jet-A-1的成本约为："}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-6 space-y-3 rounded bg-slate-900 p-4","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between text-sm","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-slate-300","children":"原油成本（Brent $115/桶）"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-slate-400","children":"$$0.88/升"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between text-sm","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-slate-300","children":"精炼、流通利润"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-slate-400","children":"$$0.12/升"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between text-sm","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-slate-300","children":"EU ETS碳成本"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-slate-400","children":"$$0.20/升"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-slate-700 pt-3 mt-3","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between font-semibold","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-slate-300","children":"现货价格（欧洲）"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-sky-300","children":"$$1.20/升"}]]}]}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-slate-300","children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"德国机场溢价："}]," 由于德国远离海运枢纽（主要依赖管道或陆运），且税收与基础设施成本较高，德国机场的航油价格通常比欧洲平均价高5-10%，即 $1.26-1.32/升。"]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-sky-300","children":"为什么德国航司承压最大"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"space-y-3 text-slate-300","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"• 地理位置劣势："}]," 法兰克福、慕尼黑等主要枢纽离海港远，运输成本高。相比荷兰鹿特丹港或比利时安特卫普港，德国机场的航油成本溢价5-10%"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"• 高税环境："}]," 德国能源税率欧洲最高之一，这直接增加了航油终端价格"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"• 短途运力占比高："}]," 汉莎集团的运力结构中，欧洲短途航线贡献了大部分航班数但利润率最低。短途飞行中，燃油成本占比30%左右（长途为20-25%）"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"• 竞争激烈："}]," 欧洲短途市场被廉价航空公司（瑞安、易捷等）垄断，价格战已经压低了票价，汉莎难以快速调整"]}]]}]]}]]}]
b:["$","section",null,{"id":"saf-inflection","className":"mt-8 scroll-mt-16","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-white","children":"SAF成本转折点：$115/桶的关键意义"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-sky-300","children":"糖基ATJ（Alcohol-to-Jet）成本分析"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-slate-300","children":"糖基ATJ是最接近商业化的SAF路线。其成本包括："}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-3 rounded bg-slate-900 p-4 mb-6","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between text-sm","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-slate-300","children":"原料（甘蔗/甜菜）"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-slate-400","children":"$$0.35-0.50/升"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between text-sm","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-slate-300","children":"能源（发酵、蒸馏）"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-slate-400","children":"$$0.40-0.70/升"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between text-sm","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-slate-300","children":"精炼与处理"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-slate-400","children":"$$0.20-0.30/升"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between text-sm","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-slate-300","children":"物流与利润"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-slate-400","children":"$$0.15-0.25/升"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-slate-700 pt-3 mt-3","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between font-semibold","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-slate-300","children":"总成本（非可再生电力）"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-sky-300","children":"$$1.60-1.85/升"}]]}]}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-slate-300","children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"关键发现：能源成本是SAF成本的最大驱动因素。"}]," 当使用可再生电力（德国风电成本$50-80/MWh）时，能源成本可从$0.60降至$0.25-0.35，使总成本下降至 $1.30-1.50/升。"]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300","children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"转折点数学："}],["$","br",null,{}],"• 油价$80/桶 → Jet-A $0.95/升 → SAF贵70% (不经济)",["$","br",null,{}],"• 油价$115/桶 → Jet-A $1.20/升 → SAF贵25-40% (可接受边界)",["$","br",null,{}],"• 油价$150/桶 → Jet-A $1.50/升 → SAF成本接近或相等 (无差异)",["$","br",null,{}],["$","br",null,{}],"$$115/桶正好是这个转折点的触发价位。结合欧盟碳价上升（目标2030年$150+/吨CO2，等效增加油价$0.40-0.50）和ReFuelEU政策约束，2028年左右SAF与传统油的成本差异可能完全消失。"]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-sky-300","children":"德国绿电优势的关键作用"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300","children":"德国风电成本全球最低（$50-80/MWh），这为本土SAF生产创造了成本竞争力："}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"• 使用绿电的SAF生产成本可降至 $1.25-1.50/升"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"• 相比其他欧洲进口SAF便宜10-20%"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"• 这给汉莎等德国航司采购本土SAF的经济理由"}]]}]]}]]}]
c:["$","section",null,{"id":"market-drivers","className":"mt-8 scroll-mt-16","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-white","children":"市场驱动因素：ReFuelEU与碳价"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-sky-300","children":"ReFuelEU 2025-2030政策路线图"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-3 rounded bg-slate-900 p-4 mb-6 text-sm","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-slate-300","children":"2025年1月1日"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-400","children":"SAF掺混比例0.7% → 年需求约4.9万吨（欧洲）"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-slate-300","children":"2027年"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-400","children":"SAF掺混比例1.0% → 年需求约7万吨"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-slate-300","children":"2030年"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-400","children":"SAF掺混比例6.0% → 年需求约42万吨 (产业转折点)"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-slate-300","children":"2035年"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-400","children":"SAF掺混比例10%+ → 年需求70万吨以上"}]]}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300","children":"这个强制性的政策约束意味着：到2030年，欧洲需要投资200-300亿欧元建设新的SAF产能。对比之下，汉莎削减2万航班（年省4万吨油）的决定，只是这个能源转变的一个微观缩影。"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-sky-300","children":"EU ETS碳价上升对SAF竞争力的助推"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"space-y-3 text-slate-300","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"• 当前碳价："}]," €80/吨CO2 ≈ $0.20/升航油成本"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"• 2030年目标："}]," €150+/吨CO2 ≈ $0.40-0.50/升航油成本"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"• 含义："}]," 传统Jet-A的隐含成本逐年上升，而SAF（特别是用可再生电力生产的）的碳成本接近零，相对竞争力快速改善"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"• 航司响应："}]," 2028-2030年间，经济学将从\"强制采购SAF以合规\"转向\"主动采购SAF以节成本\""]}]]}]]}]]}]
d:["$","section",null,{"id":"germany-advantage","className":"mt-8 scroll-mt-16","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-white","children":"德国制造优势与产业机遇"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-sky-300","children":"为什么SAF产业选择德国"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"space-y-4 text-slate-300","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"• 完整的产业链："}]," 德国化工巨头（巴斯夫、科万塔）拥有生物精炼与精细化工能力，可快速转向SAF生产。莱茵河流域的石油化工集群天然适合SAF生产。"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"• 绿电成本优势："}]," 德国陆上风电成本€50-80/MWh（全球最低）。这直接降低SAF生产的能源成本15-20%。"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"• 人才与技术："}]," 德国在生物技术、催化、碳捕获等核心技术上全球领先，这些都是SAF生产的关键。"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"• 航空运输枢纽："}]," 法兰克福是欧洲第二大航空枢纽，便利的场景测试与市场对接。"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"• 政府支持："}]," 德国与欧盟都通过贷款、补贴、税收优惠支持本土SAF。2024-2030年投入预期超100亿欧元。"]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-sky-300","children":"汉莎集团的战略位置"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-slate-300","children":"汉莎作为德国最大航空企业，有独特的战略机遇："}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"space-y-3 text-slate-300","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"• 本土供应链："}]," 可率先与德国SAF生产商建立长期合作协议，锁定成本优势与供应稳定性。"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"• 成本竞争力："}]," 使用德国本土生产的绿电SAF，汉莎可在2028-2030年实现比其他欧洲航司更低的燃油成本，形成新的竞争优势。"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"• 品牌与ESG："}]," 削减运力同时加快SAF采购，展现汉莎的可持续承诺，改善企业形象与投资者评分。"]}]]}]]}]]}]
e:["$","section",null,{"id":"outlook","className":"mt-8 scroll-mt-16","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-white","children":"未来情景展望（2026-2030）"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-4","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-sky-300 mb-3","children":"基础情景：油价$110-130/桶，SAF逐步主流化"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"地缘冲突持续，OPEC+维持减产。SAF与传统油的成本差异缩小至20-30%。ReFuelEU强制要求驱动SAF需求。到2030年，欧洲SAF年产能达40-50万吨。汉莎与其他大型航司加快采购。德国SAF生产商获得市场领导地位。预期投资回报率15-20%/年。"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-sky-300 mb-3","children":"风险情景：油价下跌至$85/桶"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"地缘冲突缓解或全球经济衰退。SAF相对传统油贵40-60%，经济学驱动减弱。但ReFuelEU的强制性约束依然存在——航司被迫采购。这实际上加强了SAF的需求确定性。规模经济快速推动成本下降10-15%。产业成熟加快。"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-sky-300 mb-3","children":"机遇情景：油价$140+/桶，能源转型加速"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"气候政策升级、碳定价加速、可再生能源投资倍增。油价高企推动SAF经济学逆转——SAF成本$1.20/升 vs 传统油$1.60+/升。航司主动采购SAF。产业规模快速扩张。德国制造业与绿色技术出口成为新增长极。这也是最有利于SAF产业的长期趋势。"}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 p-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-sky-300","children":"关键启示"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-slate-300","children":"汉莎2026年4月的削减航班决定，不是航空业衰退的信号，而是产业升级的开始。过去的航空竞争是\"规模与成本优化\"，未来的竞争将是\"燃料转型与供应链\"。那些能够快速采购SAF、建立本土产业链、掌握绿电技术的航空企业和国家，将在2030年后获得显著的成本与竞争优势。"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-slate-300","children":"对德国而言，这是一个黄金机遇窗口。现在投资SAF产业、绿电基础设施与相关技术，到2030年可实现全球领导地位。这也解释了为什么汉莎选择削减短途（利润微薄）而投资SAF——这是对未来能源结构的战略赌注。"}]]}]]}]
f:["$","section",null,{"className":"mt-8 grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-2","children":[["$","article",null,{"className":"rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/70 p-5","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-4","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-medium text-white","children":"建议执行动作"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400","children":"针对产品与研究流程"}]]}],[["$","ul",null,{"className":"space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"• 把该场景作为默认“事件冲击”模板放入 scenario registry。"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"• 在 sources 页面持续显示来源置信度、滞后与 fallback 说明。"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"• 每次重大航司事件后，复用同一页面模板发布可索引分析。"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-sm text-slate-300","children":["快速入口：",["$","$L5",null,{"className":"text-sky-300 underline","href":"/scenarios","children":"Scenarios"}]," ·"," ",["$","$L5",null,{"className":"text-sky-300 underline","href":"/sources","children":"Sources"}]]}]]]}],["$","article",null,{"className":"rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/70 p-5","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-4","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-medium text-white","children":"免责声明"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-1 text-sm text-slate-400","children":"Data and interpretation scope"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300","children":[["$","p",null,{"children":"本页用于“准实时研究支持”，不是交易系统或投资建议。当前航油数据仍包含代理源（例如 US Gulf / proxy feed），不等同于德国本地机场现货成交价。"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"当欧洲本土航油与 EU ETS 实时通道接入后，本页将更新为区域优先报价并保留代理源作为回退链路。"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"结论应结合航司实际对冲策略、税费结构和运力调整计划共同解读。"}]]}]]}]]}]
