1c:[["$","title","0",{"children":"汉莎削减2万航班背后：可持续航油成本拐点到来 | SAFvsOil"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"深度分析汉莎2026年4月削减20,000航班事件。通过解构当前航油价格、SAF成本动态、欧盟政策驱动，揭示可持续航油的竞争力转折点与德国生产机遇。2000+字深度内容营销文章。"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"SAF,jet fuel,aviation fuel,sustainable aviation fuel,Lufthansa,ReFuelEU,fuel cost analysis,EU ETS"}],["$","meta","3",{"property":"og:title","content":"汉莎削减2万航班背后：可持续航油成本拐点到来"}],["$","meta","4",{"property":"og:description","content":"深度分析汉莎2026年4月削减20,000航班事件。通过解构当前航油价格、SAF成本动态、欧盟政策驱动，揭示可持续航油的竞争力转折点与德国生产机遇。2000+字深度内容营销文章。"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://saf.meichen.beauty/analysis/lufthansa-flight-cuts-2026-04"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:site_name","content":"SAFvsOil"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://saf.meichen.beauty/og-image.png"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image:width","content":"1200"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:image:height","content":"630"}],["$","meta","10",{"property":"og:type","content":"article"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"汉莎削减2万航班背后：可持续航油成本拐点到来"}],["$","meta","13",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"深度分析汉莎2026年4月削减20,000航班事件。通过解构当前航油价格、SAF成本动态、欧盟政策驱动，揭示可持续航油的竞争力转折点与德国生产机遇。2000+字深度内容营销文章。"}],["$","meta","14",{"name":"twitter:image","content":"https://saf.meichen.beauty/og-image.png"}]]
